'''KLR-B3''' was one of four prototype [[KLR series combat droid]]s produced by the [[Army Weapons Research Department]] on the rogue [[Planet/Legends|planetoid]] [[Tembora]] in the [[Tembora Research Station]]. It was shut down after only the initial system trials due to malfunctions found in [[KLR-B1]]'s software programming which caused him to turn into a psychopath. KLR-B3 was taken by the base from the surviving members of the ''[[Maid of Sentiile]]''. It is unknown what happened to the [[Droid/Legends|droid]] after this.

